version_description:
-The latest 3D Earth function can roam every corner of the earth
-VR function, you can wear VR eyes to enjoy the beautiful scenery

- Optimized the smoothness of the earth display, and can display high-definition map
- The street view map is optimized, and the streets and areas with street view can also be displayed in China

- Add measure distance and area function
- Bug fix

-Fix bugs
-Add global camera function
-You can randomly locate a location on the map
-You can randomly locate a street scene
-Add open street map layer
